人坐<br />\n點會同你取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80018727734774a878f0f50d443ff69f1ecf73bd","tid":512039,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:26:14.000Z","msg":"乜嘢係「公眾條例」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce04ab24354274cf20ac632992ee5f28251e85e","tid":512039,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:27:33.000Z","msg":"仆街大劣狗"},{"pid":"3418693663f6e184f2f78d152ee5e82ee50f466e","tid":512039,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:29:00.000Z","msg":"睇得呢d野多好難唔憎中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}